{"tid":1992922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和你唱行動提示：攬炒交俾黑警，我地要強調黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2020-04-28T12:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T12:40:12.000Z","uid":90601,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"15972549ab1e385c560216d10109292c7efbf24f","tid":1992922,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"前題：<br />\n依家經濟已經真係好差 零售基本上收曬皮<br />\n半年前既攬炒 今日其實多少已經實現左<br />\n但係香港咁傾斜不均同肥上瘦下既環境之下<br />\n食屎既仲未係權貴同高層 而係基層<br />\n<br />\n策略：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿輕敵 避免政府經濟輿論戰</span></span><br />\n以柒婆既仆街風格 佢一定會話 經濟差唔關佢地事 佢已經宣佈復工<br />\n而係你地係商場聚集 所以搞到民不聊生 將責任推去手足度<br />\n<br />\n繆誤破解：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舊年中秋全港和你唱 一樣做到生意 商家分分鐘仲賺多左</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無黑警 根本天下大平</span></span><br />\n<br />\n解決方式：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你唱既同時，要強調黃色經濟圈</span></span><br />\n加強自己人既消費推廣<br />\n依家係「<strong>後武肺／攬炒階段</strong>」<br />\n市場復甦係必然，問題係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">領功</span></span></strong>既邊個<br />\n依場係一場民意戰，甚至會影響九月立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be water 勿輕敵<br />\n勤做文宣 信息明確 爭取民意 </span>"},{"pid":"3a50d3d1dd55d6cdcc7de09d2f296b4a1ec5d193","tid":1992922,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:10:59.000Z","msg":"Gchi!"},{"pid":"44f4bd4180019d069cc7357ec2e3b0c76eed071e","tid":1992922,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"邊個集團藍既或旗下商場多藍店既"},{"pid":"5facc0587a092a1f5c0e5df99ecda849318f4c56","tid":1992922,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal